<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Discoun3, [Merchant Name]!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .header h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #666;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to Discoun3, <%= merchantName %>!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h3>We're thrilled to have you join our growing network of merchants!</h3>
            <p>As a trusted partner on Discoun3, you'll be able to manage your store, set pricing, and list your
                services to millions of potential customers. It’s time to take your business to the next level!</p>
            <p><strong>What’s next?</strong> Get started today by logging into your dashboard, where you can add your
                first service, explore marketing tools, and monitor your sales performance.</p>
            <a href="<%= dashboardLink %>" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            <p>If you need any assistance, our support team is just a click away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Discoun3 | All Rights Reserved</p>
            <p><a href="https://discoun3ree.com/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a> | <a
                    href="https://discoun3ree.com/support">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>